channel.title: Good source?
channel.description:
This might not be the right section but it seemed most fit.
I need a very good source that I can use for my server. Preferably a Delta, because that's what I code best, but any other 317 will do. It needs to following.
[ul][li]Good economy (I can fix some stuff if it doesn't have a great economy)[/li] [li]Godswords with correct animations etc..[/li][/ul]
That's pretty much it, I went through 20 pages of the source downloads and none were up to my expectations, so if you have one, please provide me with the name, link to ad, or the link to the download for the source AND client. Thanks :)
